thread.title: Eddie happy customer
thread.title_full: Spa World Australia Pty Ltd reviewed by Eddie happy customer

author: Eddie happy customer
title: Eddie happy customer
text:
We brought the 4.5meter swim spa with 3 swim jets. It's a great Spa you can spend the time swimming against the jets to help out with the cardiovascular or the fitness which my wife luvs or you can seat back and enjoy the bubbles which seem to spend a lot of time enjoying lol. Would give it a 5 out of 5.
Regrets should have brought the dual swim spa so we could run the swim area cooler and keep the spa seats nice and hot. Cheers Eddie
